        with allure.step('选择打包带走，点击确定'):
            first_sure = base.find_element(self.xp_el.type_android_uiautomator, self.xp_el.sure1)

            base.find_element(self.xp_el.type_xpath, self.xp_el.name_the_second).get_attribute("text")
